---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
	title="实验室 — Codex 额度监控、AI 工具与工作系统"
	description="With Keni 实验室记录 Codex 额度监控工具、PMP 模拟考试、AI 记录员与实际工作流实验，包括 Windows 悬浮球和 macOS 菜单栏用量监控。"
	active="lab"
	pagePath="lab"
>
	<section class="page-intro wrap"><p class="eyebrow">AI & working systems</p><h1>把新技术放进<br />真实的工作里</h1><p class="lead">这里不收集空泛的 AI 新闻。只记录真正动手做过的工具、工作流、模型实验，以及它们是否解决了问题。重点包括 Codex 额度监控、AI 辅助记录和能进入日常工作的实用系统。</p></section>
	<section class="content-section wrap">
		<div class="section-heading"><h2>实验项目</h2><p>项目会逐步公开，涉及公司机密的实现只讨论方法，不展示受保护的资料。公开工具优先保留本地、安全、轻量的边界。</p></div>
		<div class="card-grid">
			<a class="card project-link" href="https://pmp.withkeni.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
				<span class="number live">LIVE</span>
				<h3>PMP 模拟考试</h3>
				<p>用于备考与知识复盘的独立应用，现已开放使用。</p>
				<figure class="pmp-preview">
					<img src="/images/lab/pmp-practice-preview.svg" alt="PMP 模拟考试应用界面预览，包含题库范围、题数和练习模式" loading="lazy" />
				</figure>
				<span class="text-link">打开应用</span>
			</a>
			<article class="card project-link codex-monitor-card">
				<span class="number live">WINDOWS / MACOS</span>
				<h3>Codex 额度监控工具</h3>
				<p>给 Windows 和 macOS 做的本地 Codex 用量监控。Windows 版是桌面悬浮球，Mac 版是菜单栏工具；都用于查看 5 小时与 1 周额度窗口，强调本地读取、不读 token/cookie，也不外发使用数据。</p>
				<div class="monitor-preview" aria-label="Codex 额度监控工具界面预览">
					<figure class="monitor-shot compact-shot">
						<img src="/images/lab/codex-bubble-chip.png" alt="Codex 额度悬浮球 Windows 折叠态，显示 5 小时额度" loading="lazy" />
						<figcaption>Windows 折叠态</figcaption>
					</figure>
					<figure class="monitor-shot">
						<img src="/images/lab/codex-bubble-panel.png" alt="Codex 额度悬浮球 Windows 展开面板，显示额度详情" loading="lazy" />
						<figcaption>Windows 展开面板</figcaption>
					</figure>
					<figure class="monitor-shot mac-shot">
						<img src="/images/lab/codex-taskbar-status.svg" alt="Codex Taskbar macOS 菜单栏状态，显示 5 小时与 1 周额度" loading="lazy" />
						<figcaption>macOS 状态栏</figcaption>
					</figure>
				</div>
				<span class="download-links">
					<a class="text-link" href="https://github.com/chinnkenni/codex_bubble/releases/latest" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">下载 Windows 版</a>
					<a class="text-link" href="https://github.com/chinnkenni/codex_taskbar_mac/releases/latest" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">下载 Mac 版</a>
				</span>
			</article>
			<a class="card project-link" href="https://invite.wgetcloud.ltd/auth/register?code=qQJ0" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow">
				<span class="number">FRIENDS</span>
				<h3>WgetCloud 邀请入口</h3>
				<p>给有需要的朋友自取使用。请根据自己的网络环境与当地规则，判断是否适合使用。</p>
				<span class="text-link">打开入口</span>
			</a>
			<article class="card"><span class="number">OBSERVING</span><h3>AI 记录员</h3><p>探索 AI 如何长期理解一个人，同时守住事实、隐私和表达边界。</p></article>
			<article class="card"><span class="number">PRACTICE</span><h3>生产流程中的 AI</h3><p>关注培训、资产管线与重复工作，而不只关注生成结果。</p></article>
		</div>
	</section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
	.project-link { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
	.project-link h3 { margin-bottom: 12px; }
	.project-link .text-link { margin-top: auto; padding-top: 24px; }
	.project-link .text-link::after { content: '↗'; }
	.pmp-preview {
		margin: 24px 0 0;
		padding-top: 20px;
		border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
	}
	.pmp-preview img {
		display: block;
		width: 100%;
		max-height: 190px;
		object-fit: contain;
		border: 1px solid rgba(58, 53, 45, .12);
		background: rgba(255, 253, 247, .42);
	}
	.codex-monitor-card { grid-column: span 2; }
	.monitor-preview {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: .85fr 1.1fr .9fr;
		gap: 12px;
		margin-top: 24px;
		padding-top: 22px;
		border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
	}
	.monitor-shot {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		justify-content: center;
		min-height: 132px;
		margin: 0;
		padding: 14px;
		background: rgba(255, 253, 247, .42);
		border: 1px solid rgba(58, 53, 45, .12);
	}
	.monitor-shot img {
		display: block;
		width: 100%;
		max-height: 120px;
		object-fit: contain;
	}
	.compact-shot img { width: min(100%, 150px); margin: auto; }
	.mac-shot img { max-height: 120px; border-radius: 8px; }
	.monitor-shot figcaption { margin-top: 12px; color: var(--ink-soft); font-size: 11px; text-align: center; }
	.download-links { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 20px; margin-top: 24px; }
	.download-links .text-link { margin-top: 0; }
	.live { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; }
	.live::before {
		width: 7px;
		height: 7px;
		border-radius: 50%;
		background: #6b8f61;
		box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(107, 143, 97, 0.12);
		content: '';
	}
	@media (max-width: 920px) {
		.codex-monitor-card { grid-column: auto; }
	}
	@media (max-width: 620px) {
		.monitor-preview { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr)); }
		.mac-shot { grid-column: 1 / -1; }
		.monitor-shot { min-height: auto; }
	}
</style>
